OL,3,CKlopp says he won't manage another
OL,4,CEnglish club
OL,6,FJurgen Klopp has said he would "rather
OL,7,Fstarve" than manage another English
OL,8,Ffootball club after leaving .
OL,10,FThe 56-year-old German was speaking at
OL,11,Fhis first media conference after
OL,12,Fdramatically announcing he would be
OL,13,Fquitting the Anfield hot seat at the
OL,14,Fend of the 2023-24 Premier league
OL,15,Fseason.
OL,17,FHe will leave with six major trophies
OL,18,Fto his name - and possibly more with
OL,19,FLiverpool still competing on four
OL,20,Ffronts this season.
