OL,6,FSo what are the main take-aways for
OL,7,FLiverpool fans and football observers?
OL,9,F"Whatever will happen in the future I
OL,10,Fdon't know now, but no club, no
OL,11,Fcountry, for the next year, and no
OL,12,Fother English club ever," he said at
OL,13,Fthe press conference.
OL,15,F"I can promise that, even if I have
OL,16,Fnothing to eat that will not happen."
