OL,6,FSpeculation has already turned to ,
OL,7,Fwith Bayer Leverkusen coach Xabi
OL,8,FAlonso - a former Reds midfielder -
OL,9,Finstalled as the early bookmakers'
OL,10,Ffavourite.
OL,12,FAlonso insisted his focus was solely
OL,13,Fon his current role and that he was in
OL,14,F"the right place". Former Reds captain
OL,15,FSteven Gerrard, currently with Saudi
OL,16,FArabian side Al Ettifaq, has also been
OL,17,Flinked.
OL,19,FKlopp insists he will have no input
OL,20,Fwhatsoever to Liverpool's recruitment
OL,21,Fprocess to find his successor.
