OL,6,F"The last thing they need is advice
OL,7,Ffrom the old man walking out, telling
OL,8,Fthem 'make sure you bring him in' or
OL,9,Fwhatever ` I will definitely not do
OL,10,Fthat," Klopp said.
OL,12,F"I wish this club the very, very, very
OL,13,Fbest."
OL,15,FKlopp was asked whether there was
OL,16,Fanything that might change his mind
OL,17,Fand encourage him to stay, in the way
OL,18,Fformer Manchester United manager Sir
OL,19,FAlex Ferguson went back on his
OL,20,Fdecision to retire at the end of the
OL,21,F2001-02 season.
