OL,6,F"No, nothing," he insisted.
OL,8,F"I respect Sir Alex a lot, I don't
OL,9,Fknow what drove him that time. I want
OL,10,Fto win everything this season, but it
OL,11,Fwouldn't change my mind. And if we
OL,12,Fdon't win anything it wouldn't change
OL,13,Fmy mind. It's a decision I made
OL,14,Findependent of any kind of results."
