OL,6,FKlopp had admitted in an in-house
OL,7,Finterview published earlier on Friday
OL,8,Fthat he was stepping down in the
OL,9,Fsummer because he could feel he was
OL,10,Frunning out of energy, and insisted it
OL,11,Fcould not be his style to offer
OL,12,Fanything other than 100 per cent
OL,13,Fcommitment.
OL,15,F"You have to be the best version of
OL,16,Fyourself, especially for a club like
OL,17,FLiverpool," he said.
OL,19,F"I cannot do it on three wheels, it's
OL,20,Fjust not allowed. I never wanted to be
OL,21,Fa passenger in all that."
